E=\{0<x\leq1:x\sin(\dfrac{\pi}{2x}) \geq 0\}
x\sin(\dfrac{\pi}{2x}) \geq 0
x>0
\sin(\dfrac{\pi}{2x}) \geq 0
x>0
\dfrac{1}{2} \leq x <1
2k\pi \leq \dfrac{\pi}{2x} \leq (2k+1)\pi
\forall k \in \mathbb{N^+}
\dfrac{1}{4k+2} \leq x \leq \dfrac{1}{4k}
\forall k \in \mathbb{N^+}
E=\{[\dfrac{1}{4k+2},\dfrac{1}{4k}]|k \in \mathbb{N^+}\}\cup [\dfrac{1}{2},1)
m(E)=\dfrac{1}{2}+\sum_{k=1}^\infty (\dfrac{1}{4k}-\dfrac{1}{4k+2})=\dfrac{1}{2}+\dfrac{1}{2}\sum_{k=1}^\infty (\dfrac{1}{2k}-\dfrac{1}{2k+1})=1-\dfrac{\ln2}{2}
